time_free.question_text:
For each section of time- if you can be available for at least 20 minutes in the time frame, select the day/TimeSlot. If not select no.

(I know it seems weird, we are using the Canvas API and naming each time slots' "yes" value to itself assists in programming)

ALL TIMES ARE IN PST. If you are not in Davis, you may need to convert.

Also you may need to scroll quite a bit that way --> because there are 7 days

 

Sunday Monday Tuesday Wednesday Thursday Friday Saturday
midnight - 4 am [Sun1] [Mon1] [Tue1] [Wed1] [Thu1] [Fri1] [Sat1]
4 am - 8 am [Sun2] [Mon2] [Tue2] [Wed2] [Thu2] [Fri2] [Sat2]
8 am - noon [Sun3] [Mon3] [Tue3] [Wed3] [Thu3] [Fri3] [Sat3]
noon - 4 pm [Sun4] [Mon4] [Tue4] [Wed4] [Thu4] [Fri4] [Sat4]
4 pm - 8 pm [Sun5] [Mon5] [Tue5] [Wed5] [Thu5] [Fri5] [Sat5]
8 pm - midnight [Sun6] [Mon6] [Tue6] [Wed6] [Thu6] [Fri6] [Sat6]
